# The s3-promote-cleanup image (deploy/s3-promote-cleanup/image/Dockerfile) builds with
# the repo root as context (it needs scripts/ + deploy/). Keep that context small by
# excluding heavy/irrelevant paths. This file only affects builds whose context is the
# repo root; the github-runner image uses its own context (ci/image/) and is unaffected.
.git
.work
build
images
*.img
*.img.xz
*.deb
*.tar.xz
